                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-8 pt-5" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <h3>Share your salary anonymously</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> It takes less than 60 seconds to submit your salary
                                anonymously and help others.
                            </li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> Each person who shares is doing their part in transforming
                                the hospitality industry.
                            </li>

                            <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> Knowing what others get paid affords everyone the
                                opportunity
                                to be paid equitably.

                            </li>
                            <li><i class="bi bi-check"></i> We currently have <%= posts.length%> salaries shared from
                                    people just like you. <a href="/signup"> Create an account </a> to check them out!

                            </li>
                        </ul>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- ======= End Section Five ======= -->
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ======= Section Six ======= -->
